23:07.679 --> 23:13.560
<i># When the lights started out #
# They don't know what they heard #</i>

23:14.019 --> 23:19.941
<i># Strike the match, play it loud #
# Giving love to the world #</i>

23:20.442 --> 23:26.198
<i># We'll be raising our hands #
# Shining up to the sky #</i>

23:26.615 --> 23:32.204
<i># 'Cause we got the fire, fire, fire #
# Yeah, we got the fire, fire, fire #</i>

23:32.579 --> 23:35.790
<i># And we're gonna let it burn #
# burn, burn, burn #</i>

23:36.041 --> 23:39.085
<i># We're gonna let it burn #
# burn, burn, burn #</i>

23:39.294 --> 23:42.422
<i># We're gonna let it burn #
# burn, burn, burn #</i>

23:42.506 --> 23:45.509
<i># We're gonna let it burn #
# burn, burn, burn #</i>

23:46.885 --> 23:51.431
<i># We can light it up, up, up #
